# Madabase Project Rules

- Build the platform as SSR-first Next.js app, never static export.
- Keep phase 1 database-free; tools should run in the browser.
- Use path-based i18n with locale prefixes like `/en/...` and `/zh/...`.
- Centralize tool definitions in a registry; do not duplicate page logic per tool.
- Keep SEO metadata, sitemap, robots, and navigation driven from shared config.
- Reserve ad slots as placeholders until monetization is enabled.
- Prefer composable components and data-driven rendering for future scale.
